title: DPS-BEST OF- Sep 03, 2020

description:
On Today's Episode of the Dan Patrick Show, DP visits the bubble to recap last night's action and preview tonight's games with Sports Illustrated's Chris Mannix and The Athletic's Sam Amick. Things in the Big Ten are starting to heat up, Dan gives another update from his source. Plus, we remember a baseball legend.
